<div style="margin-bottom:20px;">
  <div style="font-size:15px; font-weight:800; color:#991b1b; margin-bottom:6px;">Retrè Echwe ✗</div>
  <div style="font-size:13px; color:#5D6345;">Lajan ou ranbouse nan pòtfèy ou.</div>
</div>

<div style="background:#fef2f2; border:2px solid #fca5a5; border-radius:14px; padding:16px; margin-bottom:16px; text-align:center;">
  <div style="color:#991b1b; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1px; margin-bottom:8px;">Retrè Echwe</div>
  <div style="color:#991b1b; font-size:28px; font-weight:900; letter-spacing:-1px;">
    <%= @amount_display %>
  </div>
  <div style="margin-top:8px;">
    <span style="display:inline-block; background:#dcfce7; color:#166534; font-size:10px; font-weight:800; padding:3px 10px; border-radius:10px; letter-spacing:0.5px;">
      RANBOUSE ✓
    </span>
  </div>
</div>

<div style="background:#fff; border:1px solid #d9d6c4; border-radius:12px; padding:12px; margin-bottom:16px;">
  <div style="color:#5D6345; font-size:10px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1px; margin-bottom:6px;">Rezon</div>
  <div style="color:#2E2E38; font-size:12px;"><%= @reason %></div>
</div>

<div style="font-size:13px; color:#5D6345; line-height:1.6;">
  Retrè USD ou pa t kapab trete. Lajan an retounen nan pòtfèy Zèllus ou otomatikman. Ou ka eseye ankò oswa kontakte sipò si pwoblèm nan kontinye.
</div>
